1.
EX-1.1
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Bootstrap 5 CDN Example</title>
  <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS CDN -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-primary">Hello, Bootstrap 5 via CDN!</h1>
    <p>This is a simple Bootstrap layout.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Bootstrap 5 JS Bundle CDN (includes Popper) -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

=>USING npm
EX-1.2

npm init -y
npm install bootstrap
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Bootstrap via npm</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-success">Bootstrap 5 from npm</h1>
    <p>This page uses Bootstrap installed via npm.</p>
  </div>

  <script src="./node_modules/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>


2.
EX-2.1

a)CSS Folder
-Contains compiled CSS Styles for Bootstrap.
-Has important Key Files like  bootstrap.css,bootstrap.min.css and bootstrap.rtl.min.css
-Each key file has it's significance for styling bootstrap.

b)JS Folder
-Contains JavaScript for interactive components like modals,tooltips and carousels etc..
-Has Key Files like bootstrap.bundle.min.js and bootstrap.min.js .

c)Icons Folder 
-Contains Bootstrap Icons (a seperate library of SVG-based icons).
-Has Key Files like bootstrap-icons.css and fonts/ .

EX-2.2

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Bootstrap Example</title>
  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Your content goes here -->

  <!-- Bootstrap Bundle JS (with Popper) -->
  <script src="bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

